question: Sophia is required to submit a 235-page dissertation. She already finished writing 1/5 of the dissertation. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Sophia has already written 1/5 of the dissertation which is 235 pages*1/5 = <<235*1/5=47>>47 pages.
So, she still needs to write 235 pages - 47 pages = <<235-47=188>>188 pages.
#### 188
